01:57:22.076 --> 01:57:23.660
More than anything.

1752
01:57:24.245 --> 01:57:25.829
I want you to come with me.

1753
01:57:29.542 --> 01:57:31.793
People always say me I strong.

1754
01:57:33.629 --> 01:57:35.714
Okay. maybe Vietnam

1755
01:57:37.008 --> 01:57:39.342
I organize many protest.

1756
01:57:39.552 --> 01:57:43.221
survive two year prison.
punish me make small.

1757
01:57:43.598 --> 01:57:46.183
I only person survive TV box.

1758
01:57:46.559 --> 01:57:50.062
I walk around. no foot.
Take care for other people.

1759
01:57:50.855 --> 01:57:53.690
But I woman. Feeling.

1760
01:57:56.027 --> 01:57:59.029
I'm sorry. I really am.

1761
01:58:00.073 --> 01:58:03.241
It's so easy for me to see who you are.

1762
01:58:04.160 --> 01:58:06.411
But if I don't do this. who am I?

1763
01:58:07.455 --> 01:58:09.539
I mean. really. who am I?

1764
01:58:10.124 --> 01:58:11.958
You Paul Safranek!

1765
01:58:12.543 --> 01:58:14.086
You good man!

1766
01:58:15.213 --> 01:58:17.255
(EXCITED CHATTERING)

1767
01:58:19.801 --> 01:58:21.718
Look. Ngoc Lan. butterflies!

1768
01:58:22.720 --> 01:58:24.179
(SPEAKING VIETNAMESE)

1769
02:00:07.450 --> 02:00:09.284
I guess this is it. (SIGHS)

1770
02:00:10.536 --> 02:00:11.703
Konrad.

1771
02:00:12.705 --> 02:00:14.414
Very nice to have met you.

1772
02:00:15.041 --> 02:00:16.541
Pleasure was mine.

1773
02:00:16.959 --> 02:00:18.501
Good luck in there. Paul.

1774
02:00:29.764 --> 02:00:31.640
Take care of yourself.

1775
02:00:32.558 --> 02:00:33.642
I will.

1776
02:00:34.435 --> 02:00:35.560
You. too.

1777
02:00:36.437 --> 02:00:39.064
I will miss my funny neighbor.

1778
02:00:54.956 --> 02:00:56.289
Your Bible.

1779
02:00:59.877 --> 02:01:01.878
But it's in Vietnamese.

1780
02:01:03.339 --> 02:01:05.006
Words not matter.

1781
02:01:06.384 --> 02:01:07.968
Remember me.

1782
02:01:21.357 --> 02:01:22.983
You go away now.

1783
02:01:44.088 --> 02:01:45.380
(SIGHS)

1784
02:01:52.763 --> 02:01:55.098
(INDISTINCT CHATTERING)

1785
02:01:55.182 --> 02:01:56.599
(SHEEP BLEATING)

1786
02:02:16.329 --> 02:02:17.329
PAUL: Excuse me.

1787
02:02:17.413 --> 02:02:21.082
Hi. Uh. is it just me.
or are we walking uphill?

1788
02:02:21.584 --> 02:02:23.835
Yes. Prevents flooding.

1789
02:02:24.128 --> 02:02:26.796
- Tunde.
- Oh. hi. Paul.

1790
02:02:28.007 --> 02:02:29.466
It's just a few hours climb

1791
02:02:29.550 --> 02:02:31.343
