1796
02:03:34.573 --> 02:03:36.074
Wait!

1797
02:03:37.576 --> 02:03:38.660
No. wait.

1798
02:03:39.954 --> 02:03:41.413
Thank you so much.

1799
02:03:42.164 --> 02:03:44.207
- Wait. my bag. No. no. no.
- TORVALD: Leave it!

1800
02:03:44.917 --> 02:03:47.627
I told you nothing ever works out
for this guy.

1801
02:03:47.920 --> 02:03:50.088
TORVALD: It's going to blow. Run!

1802
02:03:53.050 --> 02:03:54.050
Paul!

1803
02:03:55.052 --> 02:03:56.261
Ngoc Lan!

1804
02:03:59.932 --> 02:04:01.099
(DOOR CLOSES)

1805
02:04:03.602 --> 02:04:04.727
(PANTING)

1806
02:04:04.812 --> 02:04:06.646
I was thinking
about what you were saying.

1807
02:04:06.730 --> 02:04:08.648
And I realized you were right.

1808
02:04:09.233 --> 02:04:10.900
I am Paul Safranek.

1809
02:04:12.111 --> 02:04:13.987
And what you were asking?

1810
02:04:15.239 --> 02:04:17.073
It was a love fuck.

1811
02:04:26.584 --> 02:04:28.209
(ALARM BLARING)

1812
02:04:37.553 --> 02:04:38.845
(STONES CLATTERING)

1813
02:05:37.905 --> 02:05:39.405
PAUL: And to think

1814
02:05:40.658 --> 02:05:42.992
one day. all of this...

1815
02:05:47.289 --> 02:05:51.876
Now maybe you understand little bit
how I feel after survive TV box.

1816
02:05:58.259 --> 02:06:00.593
When you know death come soon.

1817
02:06:01.762 --> 02:06:04.347
you look around things more close.

1818
02:06:17.820 --> 02:06:20.321
