1819
02:07:10.831 --> 02:07:12.749
PAUL: Wait here. I'll be right back.

1820
02:07:13.208 --> 02:07:15.960
I want go. too.
I want see Rosa new baby.

1821
02:07:16.045 --> 02:07:18.796
No. see the baby tomorrow. It's pouring!

1822
02:07:22.343 --> 02:07:23.343
NGOC LAN: Hurry.

1823
02:07:23.427 --> 02:07:27.764
Don't forget. we still need go see
Philippine man. take care for his arm.

1824
02:07:28.015 --> 02:07:30.350
PAUL: I know. Stop obsessing. will you?

1825
02:07:47.493 --> 02:07:50.453
(ACTORS ON TV SPEAKING SPANISH)

1826
